    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I've started a jekyll website based with the content of @bobylito's documentation here: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/tree/feature/new-site/site\n\nWe'll probably host it on `https://community.algolia.com/instant-search/` or something similar.\n\nWhy Jekyll?\n- built-in search :) (cc @pixelastic)\n- gh-pages compliant\n- markdown <3\n- ease of development with SASS, live-reload & templates\n",
